Description_lang: Tectus is unkillable as long as he is under the effects of Shard of the Mountain.He periodically gains energy, with the rate of gain increasing as he loses health.The power of Shard of the Mountain is consumed whenever Tectus channels Tectonic Upheaval, leaving him vulnerable to shattering.
AuraDescription_lang: Unkillable.Applies Accretion to himself and nearby allies every $t1 sec.
